You can get this to work with Mac by purchasing a Steingberg E-Licenser USB! 

1. Purchase E-Licenser at local music store
2. Bootcamp install to windows or install on a PC
3. Transfer the licenses over to the USB key.
4. Download Demos on the Arturia homepage
5. Install Demos
6. Open E-Licenser Control Panel
7. Transfer keys from USB to your Mac
8. Return USB Key at Music store for Refund.
